WEBVTT

1
01:25:33.901 --> 01:25:36.437 
虫子还是鸟饲料  啥
Okay, worms or birdseed? Huh?

2
01:25:36.570 --> 01:25:38.639 
开玩笑的啦  我知道你会选吐司
Kidding. I know it's toast.

3
01:25:38.772 --> 01:25:40.207 
吐司
Ha, ha. Toast.

4
01:25:40.340 --> 01:25:42.143 
其实我当时说我最喜欢吐司
You know, I was actually being sarcastic

5
01:25:42.277 --> 01:25:43.812 
只是想挖苦你
when I said that was my favorite,

6
01:25:43.945 --> 01:25:45.112 
只是稍微澄清一下
just for the record.

7
01:25:45.245 --> 01:25:46.880 
什么  你在
What? You?

8
01:25:47.013 --> 01:25:48.315 
挖苦我
Sarcastic?

9
01:25:48.450 --> 01:25:50.117 
不是吧  我知道你想说什么
No way. I see what you're doing. Okay.

10
01:25:50.250 --> 01:25:52.286 
说不定改天你可以教教我
Maybe you can teach me sometime.

11
01:25:52.850 --> 01:25:55.056 
有机会的话  如果你不忙着拯救世界的话
Yeah, maybe I will, when you're not too busy saving the world.

12
01:25:55.188 --> 01:25:58.125 
你猜怎么着  我才刚拯救完一次哟
You know, I actually just finished doing that,

13
01:25:58.259 --> 01:25:59.961 
现在闲得很
so I'm pretty free.

14
01:26:00.094 --> 01:26:02.563 
太巧了  我也很闲
Oh, no way. Because I'm pretty free too.

15
01:26:02.696 --> 01:26:05.132 
我也正好没事干
Well, I don't have anything to do either!

